# Dataset: silver_orders

## Silver Layer Purpose
Cleansed and validated transactional order dataset for revenue analytics and customer behavior reporting.

---

## Cleaning Rules

| Column | Cleaning Logic |
|---|---|
| Order ID | Remove duplicate records |
| Customer ID | Remove null customer IDs |
| Platform | Standardize platform names |
| Order Value (INR) | Remove negative values |
| Delivery Time | Remove invalid delivery durations |
| Service Rating | Validate rating range (1–5) |
| Customer Feedback | Trim text formatting |

---

## Validation Framework

| Validation Category | Rule |
|---|---|
| Duplicate Validation | Order ID must be unique |
| Revenue Validation | Order Value > 0 |
| Rating Validation | Ratings between 1 and 5 |
| SLA Validation | Delivery Time > 0 |
| Null Validation | Customer ID mandatory |

---

## Transformation Logic

| Transformation | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Convert timestamps | Time intelligence |
| Create SLA flag | Delayed delivery analysis |
| Create revenue bands | Revenue segmentation |
| Create order categories | Business reporting |
| Derive order date hierarchy | Trend analysis |

